result.execSummary:
The defendant Daniel J. Hoeschele was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Daniel J. Hoeschele is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Daniel J. Hoeschele was found guilty of Manufacture/Deliver Heroin (<3g), a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1)(d)1.
